quran[10{c,v,t}:
17,8,"ho sakta hai ke ab tumhara rab tum par reham kere, lekin agar tum ne phir apni sabiq rawish ka iada kya to hum bhi par apni saza ka iada karen ge, aur ka fir Nemat logon ke liye hum ne jahannum ko qaid khanah bana rakha hai"
17,9,haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh quran woh raah dekhata hai jo bilkul seedhi hai jo lau g usay maan kar bhallay kaam karne lagen inhen yeh basharat deta hai ke un ke liye bara ajar hai
17,10,aur jo log akhirat ko nah manen inhen yeh khabar deta hai ke un ke liye hum ne dard naak azaab muhayya kar rakha hai
17,11,ensaan shar uss terhan mangta hai jis terhan kher maangni chahiye ensaan bara hi jald baz waqay howa hai
17,12,"dekho, hum ne raat aur din ko do nishanain banaya hai raat ki nishani ko hum ne be noor banaya, aur din ki nishani ko roshan kar diya taakay tum apne rab ka fazl talaash kar sakuu aur mah o saal ka hisaab maloom kar sakuu isi terhan hum ne har cheez ko allag allag mummies kar ke rakha hai"
17,13,"har ensaan ka shagoon hum ne uss ke apne gilaay mein latka rakha hai, aur qayamat ke roz hum aik noshta uss ke liye nikalen ge jisay woh khuli kitaab ki terhan paye ga"
17,14,"parh apna nama aamaal, aaj apna hisaab laganay ke liye to khud hi kaafi hai"
17,15,"jo koi raah raast ikhtiyar kere is ki raast rawi is ke apne hi liye mufeed hai, aur jo gumraah ho is ki gumraahi ka waba l- usi par hai koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga aur hum azaab dainay walay nahi hain jab taq ke ( logon ko haq o baatil ka farq samjhane ke liye ) aik pegham Bar nah bhaij den"
17,16,"jab hum kisi bastii ko halaak karne ka iradah karte hain to is ke khushaal logon ko hukum dete hain aur woh is mein nafarmaniyan karne lagtay hain, tab azaab ka faisla is bastii par chaspan ho jata hai aur hum usay barbaad kar ke rakh dete hain"
17,17,"dekh lau, kitni hi naslen hain jo Nooh ke baad hamaray hukum se halaak huien tera rab apne bundon ke gunaaho se poori terhan bakhabar hai aur sab kuch dekh raha hai"
